                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                                        <date>Jany 18, 1849</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Isaac Leeser Eq </addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Revd &amp; dear Sir</p>\n                              <p>For some days past I have been<lb/> very unwell The cholera\n                                        attacked<lb/> me very hard but thanks to a Divine<lb/>\n                                        Providence I am again restor'd<lb/> to Health &amp; at your\n                                        Service<lb/> I instructed my Book Keeper<lb/> to answer your\n                                        Last Letter, which<lb/> he informs me he did. I must\n                                        here<lb/> confirm his words, vz, some of those<lb/> Books\n                                        are not only Insured but<lb/> appear to have been used.</p>\n                              <p>Its strange not one of the members<lb/> of the Portuguese\n                                        Congregation<lb/> seem willing to buy any of your<lb/>\n                                        <sic>Preyer</sic> Books. now I presume<lb/> If there was\n                                        none here they would<lb/> be forwarding their Orders to\n                                        you<lb/> or elsewhere for various Books<lb/> yet here they\n                                        are &amp; not a soul<lb/> needs them. I am happy to\n                                        inform<lb/> you the <add>?</add>etcher Books are moving<lb/>\n                                        I sent <persName>Emanuel Mobile</persName> 1 Doz Four<lb/>\n                                        of each price &amp; have left 7 c2.75—11 c 2 50</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jw8742m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
